## Setup Instructions

### 1. Copy Template to Production File

```bash
cp credentials.md.template credentials.md
```

### 2. Fill in Your Credentials

Edit `credentials.md` and replace all placeholder values with actual credentials.

### 3. Secure the File

```bash
chmod 600 credentials.md  # Unix/Linux/Mac
```

### 4. Verify .gitignore Entry

Add to `.gitignore`:
```
credentials.md
credentials.json
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
```

### 5. Test Environment Loading

```bash
node plugin/environment-loader.js init --verbose
```

